> """FR-14: Messenger + WhatsApp Adapter — Webhook Verification and Parsing.
  
> [FR-14] Acceptance criteria:
>   - POST /api/v1/webhook/messenger parses Messenger WebhookEvent, returns 200 OK within 3s
>   - POST /api/v1/webhook/whatsapp parses WhatsApp WebhookEvent, returns 200 OK within 3s
>   - Messenger verification uses sha256= + HMAC-SHA256(app_secret, body).hexdigest()
>   - WhatsApp verification uses sha256= + HMAC-SHA256(app_secret, body).hexdigest()
>   - Both verifiers use hmac.compare_digest() for timing-attack resistance
>   - VERIFIERS dict contains "messenger" and "whatsapp" keys
>   - Verification failure returns 401 AUTH_INVALID_SIGNATURE
  
> Citations: SRS.md:19-34, SAD.md:113-155, ADR-013
> """
  
